name: Selfish
description:
This piece is a collab with the fantastic Igor Pang, one of my favorite abstract artists on HEN! The simultaneously light and dark layers of Igor's work perfectly compliments the bright positive sounds! 50% of primary sales will be sent to Mr. Igor.
I want to see everyone win...for selfish reasons. 

Produced by Ronnie.tez
Written, Recorded, and Performed by me
Mixed by Santoro
Cover art by ezraigor aka Igor Pang
